posting_body: This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 800 Sq.
Find your new home in Kent's quiet yet accessible West Hill neighborhood at Woodland Estates.

Located just off I-5 and Highway 167, our studio and one-bedroom apartments are surrounded by trees and landscaped grounds, as well as parks, lakes and trails (including a boardwalk to Lake Fenwick Park).
Walk to numerous other activities or take one of several public transportation options with stops located close by.
Affordable living is just a short drive or train ride away from Downtown Seattle.
